                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.93/53.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">American Consul General at Monterey</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-11-03">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 3, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Chinese Legation here requests that you give such assistance as may be necessary
                    to destitute Chinese. Please comply, keeping separate account of such
                    expenditures in order that a bill may be submitted to Chinese Legation for
                    reimbursement.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
